subject: meta-fii/meta-kudo: Add obmc-console supports solssh
commitMessage:
meta-fii/meta-kudo: Add obmc-console supports solssh

1. Enable /dev/ttyS1 for host CPU console via port 2201
1. Enable /dev/ttyS3 for host SCP console via port 2203

Tested-by:
1. Load image on the Kudo BMC board
2. Use "ssh root@ip -p 2201" to enable CPU console
3. Use "~." to escape from the connection

Signed-off-by: Lancelot Kao <lancelot.kao@fii-usa.com>
Signed-off-by: Mohaimen alsmarai <Mohaimen.alsamarai@fii-na.com>
Change-Id: I3146503456f6ba10170e53c0aee6a1d957072f9a
